# Sarathy — Your Financial Companion

An AI-powered financial companion for university students and NRIs in Singapore.

Built by Aashmiin Kaur — SMU, 1st Year Bachelor of Accountancy
SEI Programme 2026

## Features
- Sarathy AI Chat (powered by Claude)
- Mood–Money Mirror
- Pause Button
- Emergency Fund Calculator
- Debt Pulse
- Goals Jar
- NRI Navigator
- Insurance Gap Check
- SIP Investment Calculator

## How to run
Open index.html in a browser, or use Live Server in VS Code.